    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved, running smoothly and looking sharp for its next adventure. If you're looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you! I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
