      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 straight-six engine. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement. The valvetrain is quiet, and the individual throttle bodies provide immediate atmospheric response. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, supported by a limited-slip variable M differential for precise torque vectoring. While the exterior shows light road-use patina, the mechanical vitals\u2014including a recently refreshed cooling system and rod bearing inspection\u2014ensure this icon is ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
